Commands used to generate the textures:

bggen darkred yellow blue red -r 45 -g 64x64  > terrainGradient.ppm

bggen black red green blue purple black -r 45 -g 64x64 > movingTargetGradient.ppm

bggen red blue green blue red -r 45 -g 64x64 > movingTargetGradient.ppm

bggen red green blue green red green blue green red -r 45 -g 64x64 > movingTargetGradient.ppm

bggen red blue green blue red blue green blue red -r 45 -g 64x64 > movingTargetGradient.ppm

